In this project, I developed a responsive and visually appealing landing page using HTML and CSS. 
The main objective was to strengthen my front-end web development skills by designing 
a well-structured webpage with different sections such as a header, navigation menu, 
content area, and footer. While working on this project, I learned how to organize page layouts,
manage spacing and alignment, apply attractive color schemes, and create a user-friendly interface.
This project also helped me improve my understanding of CSS styling, positioning,
and responsive design techniques, making it a valuable step in my web development journey.
